<subSubSection pageNumber="282" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="282">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">Note:</emphasis>
Berkutenko concluded from her study that 828.6 (LINN) and the Krasheninnikov plate both belong to what had been called 
<taxonomicName authority="(Bess.) Andrz." authorityName="Andrz." baseAuthorityName="Bess." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Schivereckia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="podolica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">Schivereckia podolica</emphasis>
(Bess.) Andrz.
</taxonomicName>
, a plant from E Russia, N Ukraine, and NE Romania, and not to the Pacific plant long known as 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.) Desv. She" authorityName="Desv. She" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Draba" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hyperborea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">Draba hyperborea</emphasis>
(L.) Desv. She
</taxonomicName>
made the new combination 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.) Berkut." authorityName="Berkut." baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Schivereckia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hyperborea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">S. hyperborea</emphasis>
(L.) Berkut.
</taxonomicName>
, and took up 
<taxonomicName authority="Langsd." authorityName="Langsd." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Draba" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="grandis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">D. grandis</emphasis>
Langsd.
</taxonomicName>
as the correct name for the 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Draba" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="282">Draba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species.
</paragraph>
